race.comment: TICKETS PLEASE (8) is better than last start when fourth (22.49) from Box 1 at this track over 388m. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from four starts. Can atone. FASCINATE PEARL (3) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing sixth over 388m this track in 22.78. Leading chance. BOLT BLASTER (1) sailed across from an outside draw last start to score an all-the-way win (17.68) at Taree Super Track in a Mix 3/4 over 300m. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Expected to measure up again. VALLEY CASH (7) put a gap on her rivals last start. Big chance on that form.
